### // My Contact Info
If you'd like to see what I'm up to or contact me, you can find me on twitter [@briansak](https://twitter.com/briansak) or [linkedin](https://linkedin.com/in/briansak).  My resume can be found [here](http://briansak.github.io/resume.pdf).

### // My Other Projects
I've been very active in the home automators community and have taken on many projects around my own home and implemented many procedures for Amazon Echo and Home Assistant.  Many of my code repositories are here on [github](https://github.com/briansak) or you can view my blog at [cybernatedhome.blogspot.com](http://http://cybernatedhome.blogspot.com).
